<concept id="concept_dts_pjd_4r">
 <title>Workspace</title>
 <conbody>
  <p>"Workspace" is a part of the BTS user interface, located between tool bar and status bar. It
      changes appearance when the user switchs between "Corpus", "Lemma" or "Thesaurus" views. </p>
  <p>The workspace consists of three or four windows depending on the view you have chosen. You can
        <xref href="oberflaeche_funktionen_e5.dita">maximize or minimize and relocate</xref> windows
      separately.</p>
 </conbody>
</concept>
